  <title>CURRENCY</title>
  <body>
    <header>
      <para styleclass="Heading1">CURRENCY</para>
    </header>
    <list id="1" type="ul" listtype="bullet" formatstring="&#183;" format-charset="SYMBOL_CHARSET" levelreset="true" legalstyle="false" startfrom="1" styleclass="Normal" style="font-family:Symbol; font-size:11pt; color:#000000;">
      <li styleclass="Normal">The currency type stored numbers with a precision of 4 decimals. Internally it contains a .Net decimal value, rounded to 4 decimals.</li>
      <li styleclass="Normal"></li>
    </list>
    <para styleclass="Heading3">Implementation</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The CURRENCY type is implemented in the structure &#160;XSharp.__Currency</para>
    <para styleclass="Normal">The Usual type of CURRENCY is 28.</para>
